            </description>
        </special-item>
        <special-item start-with="false" useable="false" special="-1">
            <name>Gray Stones</name>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[These are three large, chalky stones, which supposedly have some powerful, esoteric magical use.]]>
            </description>
        </special-item>
        <special-item start-with="false" useable="false" special="-1">
            <name>Unicorn Charm</name>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[You were given this charm by the unicorns as a reward for services rendered. It will get you past the Unicorn Gate.]]>
            </description>
        </special-item>
        <special-item start-with="false" useable="false" special="-1">
            <name>Unicorn Horn</name>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[This is the horn of the unicorn Aessoforus, who was slain by the Blood Glee Clan of giants. The unicorns you have met really want it back.]]>
            </description>
        </special-item>
        <special-item start-with="false" useable="false" special="-1">
            <name>Drake Key</name>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[You found this key in the remote lair of a family of ice drakes.]]>
            </description>
        </special-item>
        <special-item start-with="false" useable="false" special="-1">
            <name>Morog&apos;s Shrooms</name>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[These small mushrooms with red spots were found in caverns far, far below the Castle of Morog.]]>
            </description>
        </special-item>
        <special-item start-with="false" useable="false" special="-1">
            <name>Mushroom Talisman</name>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[Morog gave you this talisman as a reward. This onyx mushroom is supposed to provide protection from something called a Spore Shroom.]]>
            </description>
        </special-item>
        <special-item start-with="false" useable="false" special="-1">
            <name>Malachite Statue</name>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[With great difficulty, you managed to steal this statuette from a strange cave filled with hostile, slimy monsters.]]>
            </description>
        </special-item>
